        },
        {
          "id": "architecture-no-persisted-terminal-record",
          "status": "fixed",
          "commit": "52c333a",
          "note": "Closed via the launch prompt: the child session is explicitly instructed to compute run_readout.run_outcome(state) and write it as JSON to the terminal_location path after the showrunner reaches a terminal state \u2014 the only place such a write can originate given the showrunner itself never persists one."
        },
